en_9548175_1	“I was shot when I worked to protect the party, its leader and its policies.
en_9548175_2	Our acts are useless to the leaders of the UNP who engage in petty politics and only think about their personal gains.
en_9548175_3	Krishantha Pushpakumara further said, “One individual is attempting to become the president in 2021, while the another person is attempting to protect his position.
en_9548175_4	Another group is working to protect the leadership council.
en_9548175_5	One faction sides with the council while another sides with the leader.
en_9548175_6	They are like railway tracks that never unite.
en_9548175_7	Because of this UNP members have been left helpless and in despair.”
